commit message:
New way to avoid the ANRs of CellLayout. Previous 'hack' was not stopping the anr on some circumstances.
@unekual provided a non recursive function to make de cell search, read my comments.
Not sure yet about possible side-effects of doing this, but launcher uses the recursive function EVERY time you press MENU, EVERY time you start dragging a desktop item, EVERY time you long press an empty desktop area.... so i prefer to have a responsive desktop even if it means sometimes have to manually 'unoverlap' a widget
